paragraphs.text: kanashige ni saku hana ni kimi no omokage o mita daisuki na ame na no ni nazeka kyou wa tsumetakute
awaku hakanaku yoru ni byurarete tameiki hitotsu ochita hanabira
tsuki no kakera o atsumete yume o kazari nemuru toki no suna chiribamete mo ano koro e kaerenai
futo miageta hoshizora mata kimi o sagashite ta ikutsu yoru o koereba namida wa tsuyosa ni naru?
kisetsu wa meguri mori wa somerare kaze wa kanadete omoi afurete
aitakute itooshikute furetakute kurushikute todokanai tsutawaranai kanawanai toosugite ima wa mou kimi wa inai yo
